          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(cradle_chat_active_runs_total{job=~\"$job\", instance=~\"$instance\", runtime_kind=~\"$runtime_kind\"})",
          "legendFormat": "active runs",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Provider Hosts vs Active Runs",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "description": "provider hosts 和 active runs 的关系。provider hosts 高于 active runs 不一定错误，可能是 pin/ref/expiry；如果长期不下降，需要去 runtime snapshot 看具体 host id、ref count、pin count 和 expiry。"
    },
    {
